=Description=

Director Irena Salina spoke with FilmCatcher at the 2008 Sundance Film Festival about why more people in the West are becoming aware of the human and environmental impact of water scarcity, how reservoir privatization affects common people, and what the role of world government should be in resolving the problem before it's too late."

